            "body": "The Cocoon Collection delivers soft, enveloping comfort within a clean, architectural silhouette. Offered in open and semi-enclosed formats, it supports flexible configurations from solo lounging to small team huddles in breakout and collaborative spaces."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Designed as a modular lounge system, Cocoon blends plush aesthetics with ergonomic intent. Ideal for co-working hubs, libraries, waiting areas, and collaborative nooks, it creates cosy yet productive environments that invite comfort and focus."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Discreetly mountable under the seat modules, swivel tray tables offer convenient surfaces for devices or notes without occupying extra space."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Powder-coated metal legs ensure long-term stability while maintaining clear under-seat space for a light, uncluttered appearance."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Available in multiple colours, adjustable cushions provide enhanced back support while adding visual variety and personalization to the seating system."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Available in multiple configurations, the system adapts effortlessly to diverse layouts and workstyles, supporting collaboration, focus, and seamless spatial planning."
          }
