        "overview_sections": [
          {
            "heading": "Soft Serenity with Modular Freedom",
            "body": "With its soft curves and low, grounded profile, the Como Sofa introduces a calm, confident presence to any space. Its fluid form supports easy movement, working beautifully in both compact clusters and open layouts."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Designed for versatility, Como’s sculpted shape encourages relaxed, informal interactions. Its modular build allows creative configurations, adapting seamlessly to a wide range of interior settings."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Unlike traditional linear furniture, this collection features a continuous, curved backrest that wraps around the user, acting as a sculptural centre piece while offering a sense of psychological privacy and enclosure."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "The design pairs soft, high-texture bouclé fabric with a solid wooden plinth base, creating a sophisticated \"earthy\" contrast that physically grounds the space and adds natural warmth to modern interiors."
          }
        ],
